prodNameC: “伊敏諾德” 濾泡促激素放射免疫分析試劑
ingredientsDesc:
1.	Anti-FSH monoclonal antibody coated tubes
2.	125I labeled monoclonal anti-FSH antibody, each vial contains 370 kBq of 125I-labeled immunoglobulins in buffer with protein, sodium azide (<0.1%) and a dye.
3.	Calibrators contain from 0 to 180 IU/L of human FSH in human serum.  
4.	Control sera contain human FSH lyophilized in human serum. 
5.	Wash solution (20x), concentrated solution has to be diluted before use.
applicantName: 泰歷藥品儀器股份有限公司
applicantAddr: 台北市大同區承德路二段81號15樓
efficacy: 用於體外定量檢測人體血清及血漿中濾泡促激素之放射免疫分析試劑。
